    public interface IAccountDomainResource<T>
extends IDomainResource<T>, IAccountContext
    Account scoped domain resource. SnapBundle is a multi-tenant system and relies on this interface to ensure that all web service calls are appropriately sandboxed within the sole account of the authenticated user.
